      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun setting over the Mediterranean as you glide effortlessly in this automotive masterpiece. Its curves are a love letter to classic design, finished in a deep, lustrous coat that drinks in the light like a fine wine. Inside, the scent of heritage leather greets you like a familiar embrace, and every chrome accent sparkles with the crystalline promise of a golden era. This isn't merely a vehicle; it is a time machine preserved in a state of absolute grace. To turn the key is to awaken a mechanical symphony, a whisper of power that commands the road with unparalleled elegance. Own a piece of history that looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor of a dream.",
      "price": 48750.0,
